<br>
You should be over level 30 if attempting this solo.  If you are under, but close to 30, it is still possible, but very hard and you should be extremely well armed and have lots of arrows on hand.<br>
<br>
Spawn time varies from 5 hours 10 min to almost 6 hours.<br>
<br>
Tactics:  Harmonize Rephas or he will aggro.  Don't worry about Axe, he couldn't give a damn about Hadden.  Move along the lake a short distance in the direction opposite Rephas and snare Hadden.  Move Hadden just south of the lake and use the appropriate mixture of melee, DoT, and arrow kiting for your level.  Earring drops approx 1 in 3.  I have gone 5 kills without an earring, but I have also gotten it twice in a row.<br>
<br>
Hadden is up after patches.  If you camp out next to Hadden, you can attempt to be the first to log in and get him.  If someone beats you to the punch, at least you have the time-frame for when he will be back.<br>
<br>
Good luck.  <br>
